title: Washington State Department of Transportation, Regional Transportation Planning Organizations, Washington, 2008
name: Washington State Department of Transportation, Regional Transportation Planning Organizations, Washington, 2008
description:
Abstract:

      Polygons represent the Regional Transportation Planning Organizations (RTPOs) and Metropolitan Planning Organizations (MPO's). RTPOs are responsible for transportation planning, growth management compliance within their jurisdictions, and the development and adoption of regional transportation plans. 

Purpose: This data set is used as a reference layer for geographic information systems at the Washington State Department of Transportation.
